                   =   Clerics of Mitra Guild News   =
                   =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
 

Well, things are changing a bit around here. A few of the recent changes:

+ You can no longer resurrect players in thieves or priest.
+ Bless and Guard are self-cast only.
+ Unparalyze was removed.
+ The costs/damage/timers were changed on most spells.
